{{!< default}}

<span id="!blog" class="pull-left"></span>
<span id="!me" class="pull-right"></span>
<header id="head" class="jumbotron container-fluid" {{#if @blog.cover}}style="background-image:url({{@blog.cover}});background-position:center;background-size:cover"{{/if}}>
	<div class="blog-info row">
		<div class="col-sm-12">
    		<h1 class="blog-title">{{@blog.title}}</h1>
			<h3 class="blog-description">{{@blog.description}}</h3>
		</div>
	</div>
</header>

<section id="splash">
	<section id="whoami" class="jumbotron container-fluid">
		<div class="row section-head">
			<h1>Who am I?</h1>
		</div>
		<div class="row square-row">
			<div class="col-sm-4">
				<div class="square who">
					<div class="square-header">
						<img src="{{asset "img/umass.png"}}" height="120px" />
					</div>
					<p>I'm a freshman studying Computer Science at the
					   University of Massachusetts, Amherst. I'm interested in
                                           type and programming language theory. I'm very passionate
                                           about languages with strong type systems.</p>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="col-sm-4">
				<div class="square who">
					<div class="square-header">
						<img src="{{asset "img/github.png"}}" height="120px" />
					</div>
					<p>I'm an open source software developer. I've been
			                   programming for roughly seven years. I'm primarily a 
                                           Rust developer, but I did Java for a long time. I'm
                                           looking to get better at Haskell, too.</p>
					<div class="square-footer">
						I'm <a href="https://github.com/aaronweiss74">
						@aaronweiss74</a> on GitHub.
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="col-sm-4">
				<div class="square who">
					<div class="square-header">
						<img src="{{asset "img/earth.png"}}" height="120px" />
					</div>
					<p>I'm an Internet denizen. You can find me all over the
					   web. I'm on
					   <a href="https://twitter.com/aaronweiss74">Twitter</a>,
					   <a href="https://facebook.com/aaronweiss74">Facebook</a>,
					   <a href="https://plus.google.com/+AaronWeiss74">Google+</a>, 
                                           and <a href="http://www.reddit.com/user/aaronweiss74">Reddit</a>. 
                                           You can talk to me on <a href="irc://irc.fyrechat.net/vana">FyreChat</a> 
                                           or <a href="ircs://irc.pdgn.co/pdgn">PdgnCo</a> as awe. 
                                           You'll probably find me elsewhere, too.</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>
	<section id="whatdoithink" class="jumbotron container-fluid">
		<div class="row section-head">
			<h1>What do I think?</h1>
		</div>
		<div class="row square-row">
			<div class="col-sm-4">
				<div class="square think">
					<div class="square-header">
						<img src="{{asset "img/leaf.png"}}" height="120px" />
					</div>
					<p>The environment is cruicial. Our treatment of the
						environment is a reflection on our respect (or
						lackthereof) for one another. I'm in favor of taxation
						on carbon emissions and governmental support for
						renewable energy research.</p>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="col-sm-4">
				<div class="square think">
					<div class="square-header">
						<img src="{{asset "img/decent.png"}}" height="120px" />
					</div>
					<p>Decentralization is powerful and reliable. In politics,
						it allows government to best serve the people by
						minimizing bureaucracy. In software, it allows users
						and developers alike more freedom by preventing the
						monopolization of data. Decentralization uniquely
						empowers the individual.</p>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="col-sm-4">
				<div class="square think">
					<div class="square-header">
						<img src="{{asset "img/simple.png"}}" height="120px" />
					</div>
					<p>Simplicity is elegance. The best software, the best
						design, and the best experience are all characterized
						by simplicity. I allow minimalism to carry my design
						methodology throughout the software I make, and I hope
						that it always reflects that.</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>
	<section id="whatdoido" class="jumbotron container-fluid">
		<div class="row section-head">
			<h1>What do I make?</h1>
		</div>
		<div class="row square-row">
			<div class="col-sm-4">
				<div class="square do">
					<div class="square-header">
						<img src="{{asset "img/site.png"}}" height="120px" />
					</div>
					<p>I make minimalist websites. I favor flat designs over
						gradients and other frills. I use JavaScript and C#
						for backends, and HTML5 and CSS3 for frontends. I also
						used to do Ruby and PHP.</p>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="col-sm-4">
				<div class="square do">
					<div class="square-header">
						<img src="{{asset "img/link.png"}}" height="120px" />
					</div>
					<p>I make a variety of custom networked applications. I
						work on designing and using simple, scalable network
						protocols and writing reliable software upon said
						protocols. I mainly put this energy towards games and
						libraries for networking protocols.</p>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="col-sm-4">
				<div class="square do">
					<div class="square-header">
						<img src="{{asset "img/maple.png"}}" height="120px" />
					</div>
					<p>I make server emulators for multiplayer games. I work on
						clean-room reverse engineering network protocols, and
						building elegant and performant emulators atop them. My
						target game of choice is MapleStory.</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>
	<section id="cryptocoins" class="jumbotron container-fluid">
		<div class="row square-row">
			<div class="col-sm-4">
				<div class="square coin">
					<div class="square-header">
						<h2>BTC</h2>
						<img src="{{asset "img/btcqr.png"}}" class="qr" />
						<h5 class="addr">1GwWFMfnZf2LwEgQAUHBiGV2PdCLyQPYA6</h5>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="col-sm-4">
				<div class="square coin">
					<div class="square-header">
						<img src="{{asset "img/money.png"}}" height="120px" />
					</div>
					<p>I'm a big fan of cryptocurrencies. I support both
						bitcoin and freicoin, and I'd like to see them grow
						into something much larger. As such, if you like any of
						the things I've worked on or just want to be a really
						nice person, I accept tips to either of the wallets
						included here. Tips are much appreciated.</p>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="col-sm-4">
				<div class="square coin">
					<div class="square-header">
						<h2>FRC</h2>
						<img src="{{asset "img/frcqr.png"}}" class="qr" />
						<h5 class="addr">16X5wPMHHyUijFoqQ1Pv4N6Ds6T3XxZu2Q</h5>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>
	<section id="moreme" class="jumbotron container-fluid">
		<div class="row section-head">
			<h1><a href="#!blog" onclick="blog();">Check out my blog.</a></h1>
		</div>
	</section>
</section>

<main id="main" class="content way-up" role="main">
    {{#foreach posts}}
    <article class="{{post_class}} jumbotron container-fluid">
		<section class="row">
			<div class="col-sm-12">
       			<header class="post-header">
					<div class="post-meta">
						<time class="meta pull-left" datetime="{{date format='YYYY-MM-DD'}}">{{date format="DD MMM YYYY"}}</time>
						<span class="meta-container pull-right">
							{{#foreach tags}}
								<span class="meta">{{name}}</span>
							{{/foreach}}
						</span>
					</div>
					<div class="clearfix"></div>
        			<h2 class="post-title square"><a href="{{url}}">{{{title}}}</a></h2>
        		</header>
        		<section class="post-excerpt">
        			{{excerpt}}&hellip;
        		</section>
				<div class="read-more meta"><a href="{{url}}">Read more.</a></div>
			</div>
		</section>
    </article>
    {{/foreach}}
	<section id="backtome" class="jumbotron container-fluid">
		<div class="row section-head">
			<h1><a href="#!me" onclick="splash();">Back to me.</a></h1>
		</div>
	</section>
</main>

<script type="text/javascript" src="{{asset "js/utils.js"}}"></script>
<script type="text/javascript">
	function squareHeights() {
		$(".who").resetHeights();
		$(".who").matchHeights();
		$(".think").resetHeights();
		$(".think").matchHeights();
		$(".do").resetHeights();
		$(".do").matchHeights();
		$(".coin").resetHeights();
		$(".coin").matchHeights();
	}
	function splash() {
		$("#splash").removeClass("way-up");
		$("#main").addClass("way-up");
	}
	function blog() {
		$("#main").removeClass("way-up");
		$("#splash").addClass("way-up");
	}
	if (window.location.hash == "#!me") splash();
	if (window.location.hash == "#!blog") blog();
	if ($(".square-row").css("display") !== "flex") {
		$(document).ready(function () {
			squareHeights();
			$(window).resize(function() {
				squareHeights();
			});
		});
	}
</script>
